function e(s){return String(s||'').replace(/&amp;/g,'&').replace(/&quot;/g,'"').replace(/&#039;/g,"'").replace(/&lt;/g,'<').replace(/&gt;/g,'>').replace(/<[^>]+>/g,' ').replace(/\s+/g,' ').trim()}
function u(x){x=e(x);if(!x)return'';if(x.indexOf('//')==0)return'https:'+x;if(x.indexOf('http')==0)return x;if(x[0]=='/')return H.slice(0,-1)+x;return H+x}
var U=String(MY_URL||'').split('##').pop().replace(/\[home=[^\]]+\]/,'').replace(/fypage/g,typeof MY_PAGE=='undefined'?1:MY_PAGE);
